Package jakarta.nosql.mapping

Interface Template

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ColumnTemplate, DocumentTemplate, KeyValueTemplate
    public interface Template
    Templates are a helper class that increases productivity when performing common NoSQL operations. Includes integrated object mapping between documents and POJOs.
